widgets_values: You don't have to enter anything into the negative prompt above. Use it if you need to remove something, what get's added in the highres fix pass.

nodes.title: Highres Fix + Tiled Upscale + Face Fix

widgets_values:
Connect to Highres KSampler and Tiled Upscale sampler if you want to reduce the time it takes for each part.

DMD2 - LCM sampler, Karras/Exponential/Simple scheduler, 3-8 steps, CFG 1.

Lightning - Euler sampler, SGM uniform scheduler, ~2-3 steps, CFG 1.
If this node below (LEGACY REFINE) doesn't get installed or it's bugging out - make sure to install "Crystools" node. Then reboot Comfy and throw the json into it again.
